text: Jeong Jeom-sig (; born 15 July 1965) is a South Korean politician who was a prosecutor and lawyer. == Life == Jeong was born in Goseong County, South Gyeongsang Province. He passed the 30th judicial examination in 1986. He later served as a high-level prosecutor at the prosecution office before retiring in June 2017. He later opened as a lawyer.
